second of the selected clip and
maybe the last second as

00:19:43.920 --> 00:19:46.580
well, so you can make sure that
your anchor points are at

00:19:46.580 --> 00:19:48.300
the point you want them to be.

00:19:48.300 --> 00:19:49.770
ROMAN NURIK: One way you could
