00:19:49.770 --> 00:19:51.230
little play buttons here.

00:19:51.230 --> 00:19:53.090
So a little play button,
and pressing that

00:19:53.090 --> 00:19:54.390
plays the first second.

00:19:54.390 --> 00:19:58.010
And the play button here that
