00:20:04.190 --> 00:20:06.750
perfect view of things.

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:08.870
Another thing I wanted to
mention is gestures.

00:20:08.870 --> 00:20:12.050
So you also want to support
gestures, like multi-finger

00:20:12.050 --> 00:20:15.710
gestures and the scrolling
gesture.

00:20:15.710 --> 00:20:17.260
And if you're implementing
this--

00:20:17.260 --> 00:20:21.910
I actually just wanted to
